t values of $X_{\\alpha}$, which is the fraction of $\\alpha$-particles.\nFor $X_{\\alpha}=0$ the r-process is taking place if $\\Delta m^2_{14} \\geq 2 \\,\n{\\rm eV}^2 $, $\\sin^2 2\\theta_{14} < 0.8 $ and $\\xi_s < 0.5$. For larger values\nof $X_{\\alpha}$ the region of parameters is strongly reduced. The present\nresults are compared to results available in the literature.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Aug 2018 17:32:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-10"}
