lly, we provide a procedure to minimize the level of biased magnitude\ncorrections in maps with extragalactic imprints.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Aug 2018 18:24:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 1 Oct 2018 22:46:54 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 26 Dec 2018 22:34:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-23"}
