 matched by models that over-populate high\nrotational states. Finally, a comparison of the total band strengths observed\nacross eight dates from 1999-2016 reveals no significant dependence on thermal\nhot spot activity (including Loki Patera), on the time since Io has been in\nshadow, nor on the phase of Io's orbit at the time of observation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Aug 2018 19:41:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-13"}
