 some variation of\nthe physical parameters because their values are not perfectly known. Through a\ndifferent method, we also have found stationary and moving breathers, that is,\nlocalized nonlinear excitations with an internal vibration. Moving breathers\nhave small amplitude and energy, which is also coherent with the fossil\nevidence.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 Aug 2018 05:26:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-28"}
