. As the\nconsequence of obtained results, a universal character of self-equilibration of\ntunnel current in one-dimensional weakly linked tunnel junctions is revealed\nand studied on the level of non-equilibrium Fano factor. As well, a new measure\nof disequilibrium in such systems - the \"steady flow\" rate - is also introduced\nand discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 Aug 2018 14:53:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 23 Sep 2018 03:05:38 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 17 Aug 2019 01:10:01 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sat, 8 Aug 2020 03:06:24 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Thu, 1 Oct 2020 03:12:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-02"}
